      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u, but honestly the risk of getting super sick from the winter gloom is way more real to me than some theoretical toxicity. plus i've read that some people use even higher doses for just a few days to hit peak absorption. if i decided to just go for it and take the 50k for a bit, what would be the most effective way to do it? like should i take it with a high-fat meal or at night to make sure it actually absorbs well?",
