      "content": "Vitamin D absorption is indeed enhanced when taken with a meal containing dietary fat, so combining it with a high-fat meal is the best strategy for maximizing intake. Taking it at night is also common, but the timing won't significantly impact absorption compared to the presence of fat. Given your desire for maximum effectiveness, I strongly advise you to discuss a carefully managed, short-term strategy with a pharmacist or healthcare provider before starting such high doses.",
