    "summary": "The user is asking for advice on how to safely perform a high-dose \"loading\" regimen of 50,000 IU of Vitamin D daily to combat winter gloom. Despite the user's insistence on bypassing medical professionals, the assistant consistently identifies the risk of toxicity, explains the biological reason (fat-solubility), and repeatedly directs the user to consult a healthcare professional or pharmacist before proceeding.",
